GetOperations.Name: Get
GetOperations.Description: Gets details about the specified Analysis Services server.

CreateOperations.Name: CreateOrUpdate
CreateOperations.Description: Provisions the specified Analysis Services server based on the configuration specified in the request.

UpdateOperations.Name: Update
UpdateOperations.Description: Updates the current state of the specified Analysis Services server.

DeleteOperations.Name: Delete
DeleteOperations.Description: Deletes the specified Analysis Services server.

ListOperations.Name: GetAll
ListOperations.Description: Gets all the Analysis Services servers for the given resource group.

OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Name: GetAnalysisServers
OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Description: Lists all the Analysis Services servers for the given subscription.

OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Name: GetEligibleSkus
OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Description: Lists eligible SKUs for Analysis Services resource provider.

OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Name: CheckAnalysisServerNameAvailability
OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Description: Check the name availability in the target location.

OtherOperations.Name: Suspend
OtherOperations.Description: Suspends operation of the specified Analysis Services server instance.

OtherOperations.Name: Resume
OtherOperations.Description: Resumes operation of the specified Analysis Services server instance.

OtherOperations.Name: GetExistingSkus
OtherOperations.Description: Lists eligible SKUs for an Analysis Services resource.

OtherOperations.Name: GetGatewayStatus
OtherOperations.Description: Return the gateway status of the specified Analysis Services server instance.

OtherOperations.Name: DissociateGateway
OtherOperations.Description: Dissociates a Unified Gateway associated with the server.
